title: Federal Supplement
additional-notes: Material in this reporter written by US federal courts and agencies is in the public domain.  The publisher may claim copyright on original annotations and other commentary it adds to the US government's work.

Renewal records for some issues of this serial (including the first issue) were renewed in Periodicals volumes of the CCE; records for other issues were renewed in Books volumes.  The publisher also separately renewed the copyright for many full volumes, which may have material that has been revised since the initial publication of the issues the volume covers.
